Title: DIY
All Day Event: 'Do you ever blow a from your bottle of Miracle Bubbles and wonder if that's as big as they get? Do you wish your bubbles lasted longer? Have you ever wanted to startle neighbors with a bubble the size of a small child floating over your roof? We can help! Come learn the basics of bubble mixology- make some wands for a more vast bubble experience- and then come play as we take our new toys for a test drive after the panel!'
